abstract: "DTQEM v18.0 simulates the decay of bipartite entanglement under continuous local dephasing (σz⊗I) on one qubit. It computes concurrence and infers CHSH via S=2√2·C. The model demonstrates Zeno-like suppression of quantum correlations with increasing measurement strength E_ext. The code is stable, open‑source, and ready for academic use."
